    subagent_type='explore',
    event=TextPart(
        type='text',
        text='Here is a comprehensive read-only summary of the matching module c
ode structure across Mobile, API, Design System, Contracts, and PRD.\n\n---\n\n#
# 1. Mobile Side\n\n### Matching BLoC (`apps/mobile/lib/presentation/blocs/match
ing/`)\n\n**`matching_bloc.dart`** (112 lines)\n- Uses `flutter_bloc` with four 
event handlers:\n  1. `RecommendationsRequested` → fetches up to 20 cards via `M
atchingRepository.getRecommendations(mode:)`, emits `MatchingLoadSuccess` or `Ma
tchingLoadEmpty`.\n  2. `SwipeActionSubmitted` → optimistically removes the swip
ed card from local state (`MatchingSwipeInProgress`), then calls `recordAction()
`. If the response is a match, emits `MatchingMatchCreated` with match summary, 
previous cards, and previous mode. If cards run out, emits `MatchingLoadEmpty`.\
n  3. `MatchModalDismissed` → restores the previous card stack if any remain, ot
herwise goes to empty state.\n  4. `ExternalMatchReceived` → emits `MatchingMatc
hCreated` from an external source (intended for Socket.io push).\n- **Note:** Th
e `_onExternalMatchReceived` handler does **not** preserve `previousCards` / `pr
eviousMode`, so dismissing an externally-triggered match dialog will fall back t
o defaults (empty list + `\'nearby\'`).\n\n**`matching_event.dart`** (40 lines)\
n- Four events: `RecommendationsRequested({mode = \'nearby\'})`, `SwipeActionSub
mitted(targetId, action)`, `MatchModalDismissed()`, `ExternalMatchReceived(match
Summary)`.\n\n**`matching_state.dart`** (77 lines)\n- Seven states: `MatchingIni
tial`, `MatchingLoadInProgress`, `MatchingLoadSuccess(cards, mode)`, `MatchingLo
adEmpty(mode)`, `MatchingSwipeInProgress(cards, targetId, action, mode)`, `Match
ingMatchCreated(match, previousCards, previousMode)`, `MatchingFailure(message)`
.\n- Uses generated model `RecommendationCard` from `social_world_matching_model
s/api.dart`.\n\n### Match List Cubit (`apps/mobile/lib/presentation/blocs/match_
list/`)\n\n**`match_list_cubit.dart`** (29 lines)\n- Simple `Cubit` with one met
hod `fetchMatches({cursor})`.\n- Calls `MatchingRepository.getMatches(limit: 20)
` and emits `MatchListLoadSuccess(items, hasMore, nextCursor)` or failure.\n\n**
`match_list_state.dart`** (41 lines)\n- Four states: `MatchListInitial`, `MatchL
istLoadInProgress`, `MatchListLoadSuccess(matches, hasMore, nextCursor)`, `Match
ListLoadFailure(message)`.\n- Uses generated model `MatchItem`.\n\n### Pages\n\n
**`home_page.dart`** (410 lines)\n- Stateful widget with bottom nav (首页 / 消息
/ 我的).\n- Home tab contains:\n  - `_buildModeTabs()` using `SwModeSelector` (n
earby / city / nationwide).\n  - `_CardStackArea` (a local StatefulWidget, **not
** the design-system `SwipeCardStack`) that handles pan gestures, animations, an
d stack rendering directly inline.\n  - Action buttons (`SwActionButton` pass/li
ke) that programmatically trigger swipe via `GlobalKey<_CardStackAreaState>.swip
e()`.\n- Shows `MatchSuccessDialog` on `MatchingMatchCreated`; tapping “开始聊天
” switches nav index to 1 (MatchListPage); “继续滑动” dismisses and emits `Match
ModalDismissed`.\n- On swipe end, automatically re-fetches recommendations in th
e current mode.\n\n**`match_list_page.dart`** (110 lines)\n- Standard `ListView.
builder` with pagination loader.\n- Uses `MatchListItem` from design system.\n- 
Navigating to chat is currently a `TODO`.\n\n### Repository\n\n**`apps/mobile/li
b/domain/repositories/matching_repository.dart`**\n- Abstract contract with thre
e methods: `getRecommendations`, `recordAction`, `getMatches`.\n\n**`apps/mobile
/lib/data/repositories/matching_repository_impl.dart`** (74 lines)\n- Implements
the abstract repo using `Dio`.\n- Wraps JSON into auto-generated OpenAPI models:
`GetRecommendations200Response`, `RecordAction200Response`, `GetMatches200Respon
se`, `SwipeActionRequest`.\n- **No socket usage** in the repository layer.\n\n##
# Network Layer\n\n**`apps/mobile/lib/core/network/dio_client.dart`** (33 lines)
\n- Configures `Dio` with base URL from `API_BASE_URL` env var (default `http://
localhost:3000/api/v1`), 10s timeouts, `LogInterceptor`, and `AuthInterceptor`.\
n\n**`apps/mobile/lib/core/network/auth_interceptor.dart`** (130 lines)\n- Stand
ard token refresh interceptor: attaches Bearer token, handles 401 by calling `/a
uth/refresh`, retries pending requests, and clears storage on failure.\n\n### pu
bspec.yaml dependencies\n- `dio: ^5.7.0`, `flutter_bloc: ^8.1.6`, `socket_io_cli
ent: ^3.0.1`\n- **Observation:** `socket_io_client` is declared but **not import
ed/used anywhere** in `apps/mobile/lib/` as of this branch. Socket consumption o
n mobile is currently absent.\n\n---\n\n## 2. API Side (`apps/api/src/modules/ma
tching/`)\n\n### `matching.service.ts` (457 lines)\nCore business logic:\n- **`g
etRecommendations(userId, mode, limit)`**\n  - Redis cache key: `recommendations
:{userId}:{mode}` with 5-min TTL.\n  - Cache-stampede protection via Redis lock 
(`SET ... NX EX 10`).\n  - Validates profile completeness and location presence;
throws `BusinessException` if missing.\n  - Max distance: `nationwide` → 99,999 
km; `city` / `nearby` → 50 km.\n  - SQL query uses Haversine formula, composite 
scoring (distance 50%, recency 30%, new-user boost 20%).\n  - Excludes: incomple
te profiles, self, gender mismatches, already-swiped, existing matches, blocks.\
n- **`recordAction(actorId, targetId, action)`**\n  - Self-swipe guard.\n  - Ide
mpotent insert via unique index on `(actor_id, target_id)`; catches `ER_DUP_ENTR
Y`.\n  - Clears Redis recommendation cache on success.\n  - On `like` / `super_l
ike`, checks mutual like; if found, creates `Match` + `Conversation` + `Conversa
tionParticipant` inside a TypeORM transaction.\n  - Returns `matchedUser` info (
nickname, avatar_url) on match.\n- **`getMatches(userId, limit, cursor)`**\n  - 
Cursor pagination on `matches.created_at DESC`.\n  - Fetches other user profile 
and conversation ID per match.\n\n### `matching.controller.ts` (111 lines)\n- `M
atchingController` (`/matching`, guarded by `JwtAuthGuard` + `ProfileCompletionG
uard`):\n  - `GET /matching/recommendations?mode=&limit=` — validates mode in `[
\'nearby\',\'city\',\'nationwide\']`.\n  - `POST /matching/actions` — accepts `S
wipeActionDto`, calls service; on match, emits socket event via `MatchingGateway
.emitMatchCreated()`.\n- `MatchesController` (`/matches`, guarded by `JwtAuthGua
rd`):\n  - `GET /matches?limit=&cursor=` — returns paginated match list.\n\n### 
`matching.gateway.ts` (77 lines)\n- NestJS `@WebSocketGateway({ namespace: \'/ma
tching\', cors: { origin: \'*\' } })`.\n- `handleConnection`: validates JWT from
`auth.token` or query `token`, checks `type === "access"`, joins room `user:{sub
}`.\n- `emitMatchCreated(userAId, userBId, payload)`: emits `match:created` to b
oth user rooms.\n- `joinUserRoom`: utility for joining a socket to a user room.\
n\n### DTOs\n\n**`recommendation-card.dto.ts`** (23 lines)\n- Fields: `user_id`,
`nickname`, `age`, `distance`, `bio?`, `avatar_url?`.\n\n**`swipe-action.dto.ts`
** (10 lines)\n- Fields: `target_id`, `action` (`like` | `pass` | `super_like`).
\n\n---\n\n## 3. Design System (`packages/design-system/lib/src/...`)\n\n### `or
ganisms/swipe_card_stack.dart` (175 lines)\n- A fully functional standalone `Swi
peCardStack` widget with animation controller, pan handling, threshold (120px), 
and programmatic `swipe(direction)`.\n- **Not currently used by `home_page.dart`
**; the page inlines its own `_CardStackArea` instead (duplicate logic).\n\n### 
`molecules/swipe_card.dart` (224 lines)\n- `SwipeCard` — stateless card UI showi
ng avatar image, name/age, distance, bio.\n- Displays `LIKE` / `PASS` overlay ba
dges with opacity based on `offsetX`.\n- Supports `offsetX`, `rotation`, `scale`
, and `opacity` for stack effects.\n\n### Other relevant components\n- **`atoms/
sw_action_button.dart`** (51 lines): Circular pass/like buttons.\n- **`molecules
/sw_mode_selector.dart`** (70 lines): Segmented control for nearby/city/nationwi
de.\n- **`molecules/match_list_item.dart`** (88 lines): Row with `SwAvatar`, nic
kname, relative time (e.g. “3天前”), and chat icon.\n- **`organisms/match_succes
s_dialog.dart`** (108 lines): Full-screen modal with scale animation, avatars, “
开始聊天”, and “继续滑动”.\n\n---\n\n## 4. Contracts\n\n### `docs/api-contracts/
matching.yaml` (179 lines)\nOpenAPI 3.0.3 spec covering:\n- `GET /api/v1/matchin
g/recommendations` — mode enum `[nearby, city, nationwide]`, limit max 50.\n- `P
OST /api/v1/matching/actions` — returns `is_match`, `match_id`, `conversation_id
`, `matched_user`.\n- `GET /api/v1/matches` — cursor pagination with `items`, `n
ext_cursor`, `has_more`.\n- Schemas: `RecommendationCard`, `SwipeActionRequest`,
