vents.\n\nKey Features:\n\n-  Event-Driven Actions: Executes actions based on ev
ents emitted by the Bloc.\n\n-  No UI Updates: Doesn\'t rebuild the UI based on 
state changes.\n\n-  Ideal for: Performing side effects, such as navigation, sho
wing dialogs, or triggering animations, in response to events.\n\nExample:\n\n``
