dgets\n\n### MultiBlocListener\n\nMultiBlocListener is a Flutter widget that mer
ges multiple BlocListener\xa0widgets into one. MultiBlocListener\xa0improves the
readability and eliminates the need to nest multiple BlocListeners.\n\nMultiBloc
Listener(\n\nlisteners: \\[\n\n\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0BlocListener<BlocA, BlocAState>(\
n\n\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0listener: (context, state) {},\n\n\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0),\
