tener((pageKey) {\n      _fetchPage(pageKey);\n    });\n    super.initState();\n
 }\n\n @override\n  void dispose() {\n    _pagingController.dispose();\n    supe
r.dispose();\n  }\n\n}\n\n```## Implementing infinite scroll using the `infinite
